stx.ds.Collection<C, T>

type
interface
implements
stx.functional.Foldable<C, T>
A collection is a foldable data structure with additional methods to add and remove elements, determine the size of the collection, and evaluate equality predicates on elements in the collection.

Instance Methods

add(t : T) : C

addAll(t : Iterable<T>) : C

contains(t : T) : Bool

remove(t : T) : C

removeAll(t : Iterable<T>) : C

size() : Int
